div.p: Sure, here's a sample resume using the keywords you mentioned to impress recruiters:

p.br:
Businessman | Project Manager | E-commerce Specialist
Gurgaon, India | sushant.sharma@example.com | LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/sushantsharma

hr.p: Results-driven Business Leader with extensive experience in E-commerce, Project Management, and Digital Strategy. Proven track record of increasing sales, improving customer satisfaction, and streamlining operations. Expertise in full-stack development using React.js, Node.js, and MongoDB. Skilled in team leadership, strategic planning, and cross-functional collaboration. Adept at delivering high-impact projects on time and within budget, with a keen eye for optimization and growth.

li.p: Full Stack Development (React.js, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB)
Digital Marketing (SEO/SEM, Social Media, Content Creation)
Led a team of 15 staff members to improve service efficiency, resulting in a 20% increase in customer satisfaction and a 15% reduction in operational costs.
Streamlined inventory management by implementing a cloud-based system, improving stock accuracy and reducing wastage by 25%.
Developed and implemented a digital marketing strategy, increasing online orders by 30% and social media engagement by 50% within six months.
Initiated new payment integration for online ordering system, enhancing customer experience and boosting revenue by 15%.
Orchestrated the development of an advanced e-commerce website using React.js and Node.js, achieving 15% faster load times and increasing user retention by 20%.
Managed cross-functional teams of designers, developers, and marketing professionals, delivering projects on time and under budget by 10%.
Implemented Agile project management techniques, ensuring effective resource allocation and meeting milestones consistently.
Optimized the checkout process, increasing conversion rates by 12% through UX improvements and seamless payment integrations.
Developed and executed a digital marketing campaign that resulted in a 40% increase in lead generation and 30% higher sales.
Improved SEO and SEM strategies, leading to a 25% increase in website traffic and improving the overall search engine ranking.
Collaborated with stakeholders to understand client needs, which led to the development of customized marketing strategies that boosted brand visibility.
Mentored junior marketing staff, fostering a collaborative work environment and improving team productivity by 20%.

p.br: DPG Degree College, Gurgaon | Expected Graduation: 2025

li.p: Developed an advanced AI-based image enhancement tool that leverages machine learning algorithms for automatic image improvements.
Reduced processing time by 20% through optimization techniques and cloud integration.
Hobbies: Traveling, Learning new technologies, Playing chess

hr.p: This resume uses a mix of technical, managerial, and soft skills, backed by quantifiable results. It includes action verbs and keywords like "increased," "managed," "streamlined," "developed," and "led" to showcase initiative and leadership. It also highlights technical expertise, industry-specific knowledge, and project experience, ensuring it grabs the attention of both recruiters and Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS).
